Ubuntu 問題處理

[Q]
安裝過程中發生: 無法安裝 busybox-initramfs
[Solve]
使用English語系安裝

[Q]
# rails server 時發生
There was an error while trying to load the gem 'uglifier'. (Bundler::GemRequireError)
[Solve]
# sudo apt-get install nodejs
資料來源：
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/34420554/there-was-an-error-while-trying-to-load-the-gem-uglifier-bundlergemrequire

[Q]
# rails server --binding=172.16.129.30 時發生
cannot load such file rails/commands
[Solve]
把Gemfile內容貼到new myapp的Gemfile下方
